'''坡的敬酒者'''是指自1949年起，直至2009年每年都會到[[愛倫·坡|愛倫·坡]]墓前拜祭的神秘人。[[File:PoeGrave-withCognac.jpg|thumb]]
==簡介==
坡的敬酒者自1949年，即愛倫·坡逝世一百周年起，每年的1月19日的午夜至清晨時分，都會帶同三枝紅玫瑰和半支[[干邑白蘭地|干邑白蘭地]]到坡位於[[巴爾的摩|巴爾的摩]]西敏墓園的墓前拜祭，從來無人知道這位來訪者帶同三枝紅玫瑰和半支-{干}-邑白蘭地的原因，不過這個神秘人維持了這項神秘的傳統超過六十年<ref>{{Cite web|title=爱伦·坡的墓前 神秘人今年没来|url=http://news.idoican.com.cn/cdsb/html/2010-01/21/content_49744905.htm|accessdate=2019-12-18|date=2010-01-21|publisher=成都商报|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205093323/http://news.idoican.com.cn/cdsb/html/2010-01/21/content_49744905.htm|archivedate=2010-12-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直至2010年，坡的敬酒者沒有再出現<ref>{{cite news | title = Mysterious Poe toaster fails to arrive for birthday tradition | url = http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bal-poe-toaster0119,0,2325798.story | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Baltimore Sun | publisher = Tribune Company | date = January 19, 2010 | accessdate = January 19, 2010 | dead-url = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120720145312/http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bal-poe-toaster0119,0,2325798.story | archivedate = 2012年7月20日 }}</ref> ，一般被理解為坡的敬酒者在坡的200周年冥壽後不再拜祭，2011年坡的敬酒者亦沒有出現，愛倫·坡故居紀念館的館長傑夫·傑若姆表示，會再觀察多一年才決定這項神秘的傳統是否正式結束<ref name="no show">{{cite news | title = Tell-tale letdown: Poe visitor again a no-show | url = http://www.wtop.com/?sid=2237199&nid=114 | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = WTOP News | date = January 19, 2011 | accessdate = January 19, 2011 | archive-date = 2015-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150605233627/http://wtop.com/?sid=2237199&nid=114 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

==神秘身分==
坡的敬酒者的身分一直無人知曉，至今只有一個人聲稱自己是坡的敬酒者，不過一般人都不認同。2007年，威斯敏斯特礼堂一位前历史学家92歲的山姆·波波拉（Sam Porpora）自稱自己就是坡的敬酒者<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.artxun.com/banhua-1536-7675483.shtml |title=60年神秘传统 今晨意外消失 |access-date=2011-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914081413/http://news.artxun.com/banhua-1536-7675483.shtml |archive-date=2016-09-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，自70年代起就到巴爾的摩拜祭，希望喚回大眾對愛倫·坡的關注<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | title = Edgar Allan Poe fan takes credit for graveyard legend | url = http://www.usatoday.com/life/books/news/2007-08-15-poe-fan_N.htm | agency = USA Today | newspaper = USA Today | publisher = USA Today | date = August 15, 2007 | accessdate = January 19, 2010 | first = Wiley | last = Hall | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604064746/http://www.usatoday.com/life/books/news/2007-08-15-poe-fan_N.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。但他的說辭很快就受到質疑，傑夫·傑若姆指坡的敬酒者最早的記載可追溯至1949年的巴爾的摩晚報<ref name="tucker">Tucker, Abigail. [http://www.baltimoresun.com/entertainment/custom/today/bal-to.poetoaster15aug15,0,738578.story?coll=bal_tab01_layout  ''Who knows who started Poe toast?''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/entertainment/custom/today/bal-to.poetoaster15aug15,0,738578.story?coll=bal_tab01_layout |date=20070930044811 }}. Baltimore Sun. 15 August 2007.</ref>，因此認為這位70年代才出現的並非真正的坡的敬酒者。

==留言==
自1993年起，坡的敬酒者間中會留下神秘的字條，1993年他留下的字條上寫上「火炬會傳承下去」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-01/21/content_7460452.htm |title=神秘人數十年敬酒愛倫·坡墓前 |accessdate=2011-12-02 |archive-date=2008-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080122184849/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-01/21/content_7460452.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1998年，另一張字條聲明最初的坡的敬酒者已經逝世，會由其兒子接任<ref name="washtimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2004/jan/19/20040119-100633-6879r/|title='Toaster' rejects French cognac at Poe's grave|publisher=Washington Times|accessdate=2009-01-20|archive-date=2009-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129204507/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2004/jan/19/20040119-100633-6879r/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2001年，坡的敬酒者在[[超級盃|超級盃]]的決賽前留言，呼籲[[紐約巨人|紐約巨人]]擊敗[[巴爾的摩烏鴉|巴爾的摩烏鴉]]，諷刺的是，這支取名自愛倫·坡詩作[[烏鴉_(詩)|烏鴉]]的球隊贏得首次超級盃。2004年，坡的敬酒者最後一次留言，時值[[伊拉克戰爭|伊拉克戰爭]]，[[法国|法国]]与[[美国|美国]]關係變得緊張，字条上写着爱伦·坡的墓地容不下法国[[干邑白蘭地|干邑]]。

